---
title: Maple-Mustard Kale Salad with Carrot, Apple and Hemp Hearts
description: Maple syrup is the ingredient that comes to mind when one talks about Canadian cuisine. This Canada Day, celebrate with our tasty combination of a maple-mustard dressing, hemp hearts and plenty of fresh veggies and fruit.
